{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You ever heard of the Wochenblatt?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like the paper of the week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Is that it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was a Jewish leftist paper under Joe-- Joe Gershman and Sam Lipschitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever heard of this because they were leading-- leading party members and elitists of the-- in the-- in the Jewish progressive, leftist movement.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I found out only-- I have to tell you this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two years later, how did it happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every week when we closed the papers, it was-- at that time, we were already just a weekly paper.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every-- after event on the press, I was in charge, because the leading-- leading people, leading personnel on our paper and our organization, they just-- they just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went hiding before they were arrested and then interned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You heard about this internment in-- in Petawawa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were only [? six ?] [? of the ?] leading people in the Communist Party and this leading leftist organization were interned.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I was-- I was left there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was holding the management of the paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I finished the paper, I just-- I just disappeared, because it went right to the-- right to the-- right to the censor, the paper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they censored the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was so something, you see-- put a-- a padlock on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we just kept surviving, and we went along and along, and soon found out that-- that outside was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Call it the Wochenblatt, is that thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I looked up the [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How-- how-- how come?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they couldn't give it an answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and might as well tell you now how it happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939, in the summer of 1939, somebody knocked on-- on the door of-- no, 1940.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
